name: Late Night Window Still Life 500,000
description: This is a Tribute to John Karel's window still life collection, i really a big fan of him because his work is inspires me to do a cool aesthetic artwork, and also i want to celebrate for 500,000 minted Hic Et Nunc NFT. Hic Et Nunc have been the best NFT Marketplace and also have an awesome community that supporting and helping each other. This is my gift for Hic Et Nunc. Thank you so much for giving us the beautiful place to live.
